data.description: Perfect location, PRICED TO SELL just in time for the HOLIDAYS and NEW YEAR! Adorable, updated, spacious 3 bedroom brick ranch home boasts over 2000+ square feet, tons of living space, oversized bedrooms, flex room/office space (can be used as 4th bedroom), NEW carpet (11/2023), NEW water heater (11/2023), modern kitchen with all the bells and whistles-stainless steel appliances, tile backsplash (renovated 2021), separate dining room, bright sunroom overlooking fenced in private backyard, with almost 1/2 acre, easy access to shopping, highway, Fort Bragg and so much more! Grab it before it's gone!
